.TH "crc16" 9 "crc16" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
crc16 \- compute the CRC-16 for the data buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u16" crc16
.BI "(u16 crc "  ","
.BI "u8 const *buffer "  ","
.BI "size_t len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crc" 12
previous CRC value
.IP "buffer" 12
data pointer
.IP "len" 12
number of bytes in the buffer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the updated CRC value.
